To go to local theme folder
	cd C:\Users\USER\Desktop\Folder Name

To ctreate directory/subfolder
	mkdir NewFolderName
	
To Create New Theme on the folder/Store: 
   theme new --password=[your-password] --store=[your-store.myshopify.com] --name=[theme name]

To get all the installed theme ID list: 
   theme get --list -p=[your-password] -s=[your-store.myshopify.com]

To get into the existant theme for work:
   theme get -p=[your-password] -s=[your-store.myshopify.com] -t=[theme ID]


To upload all the local envinorment files into the store theme
	theme deploy

To To update local changes automatically
	theme watch


To edit files:
	need "visual studio code"
	Extensio : Shopify highlight, emmet
	
To enable emment in liquid file:
	Go to file>preferences>settings> search emment and edit setting.json and past the code
	{
    	"editor.minimap.enabled": false,
    	"breadcrumbs.enabled": false,
    	"editor.wordWrap": "on",
    	"emmet.includeLanguages": { "liquid": "html" },
    	}
